data.title: A Better, Cheaper Fit for the Knicks Than Carmelo Anthony
data.meta_description: According to the Charlotte Observer, a pair of NBA executives have confirmed that the Bobcats are gauging the trade value of everyone on the roster, including co-captains Stephen Jackson and Gerald Wallace.
